reviewText: Very, very enjoyable ! I've  seen both William Mitchell & Zora- Arcus Duntov in books & magazines I've owned, but my 1st time I've ever seen & heard them speak ! I  highly recommend this program !!
The book was in good condition and has lots of useful information in it
gave it to a corvette collector.  He enjoyed it
